  "prompt": "Which earphones are better under 2000?",
  "response": "There are several good earphones available under \u20b92000 in India. Here are some top recommendations:\n\n1. **boAt Airdopes 141**\n   - **Price:** Around \u20b91,099\n   - **Features:** Bluetooth 5.0, up to 42 hours of total playtime, IP7 water resistance, and good sound quality for the price.\n\n2. **Realme Buds Q2**\n   - **Price:** Around \u20b91,999\n   - **Features:** Active Noise Cancellation (ANC), up to 28 hours of total playtime, and decent sound quality.\n\n3. **Noise Air Buds Mini**\n   - **Price:** Around \u20b91,799\n   - **Features:** Up to 20 hours of playtime, IPX5 water resistance, and a compact design.\n\n4. **JBL C100TWS**\n   - **Price:** Around \u20b91,999\n   - **Features:** JBL signature sound, up to 21 hours of total playtime, and touch controls.\n\n5. **pTron Bassbuds Duo**\n   - **Price:** Around \u20b9799\n   - **Features:** Up to 32 hours of total playtime, IPX4 water resistance, and good bass response.\n\nEach of these options offers a good balance of features and performance within your budget. The best choice for you would depend on your specific needs, such as battery life, water resistance, or sound quality.",
